### Create session (basic)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "userGameId": "1",
  "players": [
    { "name": "Abi", "isWinner": true },
    { "name": "Michael", "isWinner": false }
  ]
}

### Create session (with custom date)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "userGameId": "709408eb-7c17-40a3-9227-25b97d6f7ce8",
  "date": "2026-04-10T19:00:00.000Z",
  "players": [
    { "name": "Abi" },
    { "name": "Michael", "isWinner": true }
  ]
}

### Get all sessions for user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sessions?userId=1

### Get sessions for a specific game
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sessions?userId=1&userGameId=1